  "text": "If an entity were perfectly balanced on this planet with respect to the Law of One, would he undergo the aging process? I am Ra. A perfectly balanced entity would become tired rather than visibly aged. The lessons being learned, the entity would depart. However, this is appropriate and is a form of aging which your peoples do not experience. The understanding comes slowly, the body complex decomposing more rapidly.",
